udtcat depends on libudt. to install the library and udtcat, please invoke the following commands

Debain and Ubuntu 
------------------
$ sudo   apt-get   update
$ sudo   apt-get   install libudt-dev #install deps
$ make # build the program
$ sudo   make   install # install the program

Fedora, Centos, and Red hat
----------------------------
$ sudo   yum   install udt-devel
$ make # build the program
$ sudo   make   install # install the program


* to uninstall the program 
$ sudo   make   uninstall

* please read the manual for the progam usage
$ man udtcat
